text:
I just listened to it again after reading your comment, and I don't hate it quite so viscerally as I did when I first wrote that comment. I suspect that after listening to so much video game music then getting slapped with something so dramatically different had a lot to do with it. This could be one of those acquired taste styles where the first time it seems awful, but repeated listens and you start to "get it" and accept it. 

On a video game playlist though, it slapped me like a rotten fish at dinner time.
